What is Animal Slaughter?

Simply put, animal slaughter refers to the killing of animals. Enacted for food, for clothes, and sadly—for fun, animal slaughter

is a uniquely human activity. So often, it’s also uniquely cruel. To make matters worse, these innocent creatures lead lives of

incredible pain before their untimely deaths, full of disease & trauma.
